{# HyperWeave Receipt Frame — Paradigm-dispatched.

   Economics + context-window proof (the receipt specimen). The receipt resolver
   (compose/resolvers/receipt.py) folds the receipt/1 payload into one pure
   dataclass per zone with every coordinate pre-computed; these partials only
   stamp pre-computed values — zero arithmetic in Jinja (project invariant).

   Paradigms:
     "primer" → primer genome, 8 chromatic variants (porcelain flagship);
                geometry byte-identical across variants, palette from the
                genome's per-variant receipt_* fields.
     "raw"    → thermal register-tape receipt (Workstream F).

   Extends document.svg.j2 (root SVG + data-hw-* attrs + metadata + style). #}
{% extends "document.svg.j2" %}

{% block defs %}
{% include "frames/receipt/" ~ (paradigm | default("primer")) ~ "-defs.j2" %}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
{% include "frames/receipt/" ~ (paradigm | default("primer")) ~ "-content.j2" %}
{% endblock %}
